## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1 вЂ” Foundation (Step 1-4)
- [ ] **Step 1:** Scaffold Vite + React 18 + TypeScript project
- [ ] **Step 2:** Install all dependencies (Tailwind, Framer Motion, GSAP, Zustand, TanStack Query, Howler, Supabase, etc.)
- [ ] **Step 3:** Configure Tailwind + CSS Variables design system (colors, fonts, spacing tokens)
- [ ] **Step 4:** Set up `tsconfig.json`, `vite.config.ts`, PWA plugin, path aliases

### Phase 2 вЂ” Core Layout & Routing (Step 5-7)
- [ ] **Step 5:** `MobileLayout.tsx` вЂ” App shell (TopBar, BottomNav, MiniPlayer slot)
- [ ] **Step 6:** `App.tsx` вЂ” QueryClient + Router + lazy-loaded pages
- [ ] **Step 7:** `BottomSheet.tsx` вЂ” Reusable swipe-to-close bottom sheet (Framer Motion)

### Phase 3 вЂ” Global State (Step 8-10)
- [ ] **Step 8:** `usePlayerStore.ts` вЂ” Full Zustand player store (track, queue, play/pause, volume, loop, shuffle, history)
- [ ] **Step 9:** `useThemeStore.ts` вЂ” Dynamic color store (dominant, vibrant, muted colors from album art)
- [ ] **Step 10:** `useAuthStore.ts` вЂ” Supabase session store

### Phase 4 вЂ” Audio Engine (Step 11-12)
- [ ] **Step 11:** `useAudioEngine.ts` вЂ” Howler.js hook (play, pause, seek, volume, events, background play)
- [ ] **Step 12:** `useMediaSession.ts` вЂ” Web Media Session API for lock screen / notification controls

### Phase 5 вЂ” YouTube Integration (Step 13-15)
- [ ] **Step 13:** `api/search.ts` вЂ” Vercel Edge Function: YouTube Data API proxy + Upstash Redis cache
- [ ] **Step 14:** `api/trending.ts` вЂ” Vercel Edge Function: trending music proxy + cache
- [ ] **Step 15:** `services/youtube.ts` + `useSearch.ts` вЂ” TanStack Query hooks

### Phase 6 вЂ” The Premium Player (Step 16-20) в­ђ CRITICAL
- [ ] **Step 16:** `VinylRecord.tsx` вЂ” Photorealistic vinyl with GSAP spin, album art center label
- [ ] **Step 17:** `Tonearm.tsx` вЂ” Mechanical tonearm with SVG + GSAP rotation on play/pause
- [ ] **Step 18:** `MiniPlayer.tsx` вЂ” Sticky bottom mini player with Framer Motion expand animation
- [ ] **Step 19:** `FullscreenPlayer.tsx` вЂ” Full player sheet with vinyl, controls, seek bar
- [ ] **Step 20:** `useColorExtractor.ts` вЂ” node-vibrant в†’ CSS variable injection в†’ theme transition

### Phase 7 вЂ” Panda Mascot (Step 21-22) в­ђ DIFFERENTIATOR
- [ ] **Step 21:** `PandaMascot.tsx` вЂ” SVG panda with Framer Motion reactions (nod, blink, sleep, shades)
- [ ] **Step 22:** `usePandaState.ts` вЂ” Maps audio state (BPM, energy, pause) to panda animations

### Phase 8 вЂ” Pages (Step 23-27)
- [ ] **Step 23:** `HomePage.tsx` вЂ” Hero, trending carousel, mood grid, recently played
- [ ] **Step 24:** `SearchPage.tsx` вЂ” Search bar + results
- [ ] **Step 25:** `LibraryPage.tsx` вЂ” Playlists + liked songs (Supabase)
- [ ] **Step 26:** `PlaylistPage.tsx` вЂ” Individual playlist view
- [ ] **Step 27:** `LyricsPanel.tsx` вЂ” Lyrics via `/api/lyrics` proxy

### Phase 9 вЂ” Auth (Step 28-29)
- [ ] **Step 28:** Supabase auth setup (magic link + Google OAuth)
- [ ] **Step 29:** `LoginSheet.tsx` вЂ” Bottom sheet sign in UI

### Phase 10 вЂ” PWA + Capacitor (Step 30-31)
- [ ] **Step 30:** PWA manifest, service worker, offline shell
- [ ] **Step 31:** `capacitor.config.ts` вЂ” Pre-configured for iOS/Android wrapping

